# Sonarr path mapping template
#
# Format:
#   <nas-path-prefix>=<sonarr-path-prefix>
#
# Rules:
# - One mapping per line
# - Blank lines and lines starting with # are ignored
# - Use absolute path prefixes only
# - Longest matching NAS prefix should win when translating
#
# Examples:
# /tv=/data/tv
# /tv2=/data/tv-archive
# /tv3=/mnt/usb-tv
# /tvnas2=/mnt/remote-tv
